high_descs: Go to the stove across the room.
Pick up the pan on the right side of the stove.
Turn around, bring the pan to the fridge on your left.
Chill the pan in the fridge.
Take the chilled pan from the fridge, turn around, bring it to the table in front of you.
Put the chilled pan on the table, right of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled pan on the table.
